ČThis bench celebrates 21 years of Mothers For Peace
Thanks to our founders Lucy Behenna and Marion Mansergh
World peace will come through the will
Of ordinary people like yourself"╝
╣Joseph Rifkind & Renee Rifkind
Walked and sat here every day, it was their special place.
They are remembered by their children:
Marion, Gabrielle and Charles
and their 10 grandchildren"╝
╣Sweet Thames, run softly, till I find my song

For Jon who loved this river,
From Madeleine who loved Jon
And from Joshua his son

The Hon Jonathan James Lewin 20.5.1959-10.5.2000"Š
